Package: rmdGrading
Type: Package
Title: Insert grading comments into an RMarkdown or Quarto document
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(
  given = "Jonathan", 
  family = "Gilligan",
  email = "jonathan.gilligan@vanderbilt.edu",
  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1375-6686"),
  role = c("cre", "aut")
  )
Description: Inserts "`::: {.comment}`" divs into an RMarkdown document 
  to add comments when grading an assignment and inserts
  R code blocks with `grade-src`, `grade-out`, `grade-msg`, 
  `grade-warn`, and `grade-err` classes.
